title: The Who DLC for Rocksmith 2014
description:
This torrent contains the The Who dlc for Rocksmith 2014.

To install this dlc:

- Copy the files from the .rar into your dlc folder (default location: C:Program Files (x86)UbisoftRocksmith 2014dlc)

- Add the following IDs to your 'skidrow.ini' file, located in your Rocksmith 2014 root folder.

41=258372
42=258373
43=258374
44=258375
45=258376

Credits go to kdobbs73

Enjoy the dlc!
